This is a HIVE(hadoop) admin and query tool written in php

It can simply use like phpMyAdmin, and you should not to config any php options when install, it can use 99% functions by php ./configure --enable-socket

Program development environment:

CentOS 5.4
Hadoop-0.20.203.0
Hive 0.7.1
Fusefs 2.7.4
Fuse-dfs
php 5.3.8
nginx 1.0.10

Can be support with:
Linux,FreeBSD,Windows with php 5.3+ and nginx 1.0+
But you must hive a hive-cli on the machine which put phpHiveAdmin on it.

------------------------Chinese 中文说明-----------------------
这是一个用php写成的Hive(hadoop)查询管理工具

可以像phpMyAdmin那样轻松的使用，并且不需要任何额外的php选项支持，仅仅使用php ./configure --enable-socket就可以使用99%的功能。
程序开发环境

CentOS 5.4
Hadoop-0.20.203.0
Hive 0.7.1
Fusefs 2.7.4
Fuse-dfs
php 5.3.8
nginx 1.0.10

已验证可以被下列操作系统所支持，但你必须有一个hive的可执行程序在本机。
Linux,FreeBSD,Windows with php 5.3+ and nginx 1.0+ .